race.comment: NINA SIYAN (5) boasts a strong record this journey here with two wins and three minors from six tries. Hit the frame latest (19.16) when second at this track in a Grade 6. Expected to go close. IRONGATE EXPRESS (4) was game in defeat off the inside draw last start, finishing second and beaten 1.5 lengths (17.11) behind Temple Of Gold at this track. Must be included in calculations. MISS MOMENTUM (3) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 3.5 lengths into third (22.22) at Q Lakeside in a Grade 6 over 390m. The form out of her last race has been franked. Must be included in calculations. ZABDON NO DOUBT (2) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.
